&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Construct complex financial models and valuation analyses&lt;/strong&gt; to provide data-driven recommendations on potential targets, divestitures, and strategic investments; including modeling funding scenarios and capital structure impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Orchestrate cross-functional due diligence&lt;/strong&gt; with Product, Engineering, and GTM teams to identify potential integration risks and validate synergy opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Develop strategically-focused project plans&lt;/strong&gt; that align departmental goals with long-term business objectives and multi-quarter value add.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Monitor industry trends and competitor activity&lt;/strong&gt; to identify and prioritize market opportunities that capitalize on emerging customer needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support investor relations and board materials where M&amp;amp;A, competitive, or strategic context adds value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optimize internal M&amp;amp;A processes and workflows&lt;/strong&gt; to increase the efficiency and scalability of the Corporate Development function.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Guide and mentor junior team members&lt;/strong&gt; formally and informally to build a high-performing, inclusive culture within the department.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
