&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Breadth:&lt;/strong&gt; A deep understanding of &lt;strong&gt;end-to-end M&amp;amp;A execution&lt;/strong&gt;, expert-level &lt;strong&gt;financial modeling and valuation&lt;/strong&gt;, and significant experience in &lt;strong&gt;market landscaping/strategic analysis&lt;/strong&gt; within the technology or cloud sector.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The &quot;Human&quot; Element:&lt;/strong&gt; Advanced &lt;strong&gt;Executive Communication&lt;/strong&gt; skills; the ability to translate complex deal structures into compelling business narratives for senior leadership and board members.&lt;/li&gt;
