&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the preparation, review, and tie-out of SEC filings (Forms 10-K, 10-Q, 8-K), XBRL exhibits, and coordination of tie out and review of quarterly investor/earnings materials and annual proxy.&lt;/li&gt;
