&lt;li&gt;B.S. in Accounting or Finance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Active CPA license is strongly preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of U.S. GAAP and experience researching and drafting financial statements&lt;/li&gt;
